{"tid":210182,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"德國exchange一問","createTime":"2017-04-20T17:46:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-12T05:54:33.000Z","uid":10620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"12538954ea6797e3e78ff501888c7bd510a00a57","tid":210182,"uid":10620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T17:46:29.000Z","msg":"想知去嗰邊exchange如果德文最起碼去到咩程度先夠洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> uni上堂通常係英文定德文教書<br />\n同埋有冇話去邊個城市exchange會比較多野玩同小岐視<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd2edafde3dafdbee552b05299c1d44bc2e2106c","tid":210182,"uid":36546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T18:04:11.000Z","msg":"啲人英文好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c3e6c2d1997ad15cff083258787bbe93573ac79","tid":210182,"uid":10620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T18:15:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>啲人英文好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我知呀 有同過個德國妹同tute<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb67d4f1bebecc3af96e493804fcd3d12493ce15","tid":210182,"uid":4596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T20:36:20.000Z","msg":"我女人都係想去德國exchange,佢好鍾意好鍾意學新language <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"096ea1436940f37cfec3e439c68f05234b8f378d","tid":210182,"uid":4596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T20:41:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我女人都係想去德國exchange,佢好鍾意好鍾意學新language <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n未完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但因為有啲事我搞到佢學唔到佢想學嘅Italian<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我到而家都好矛盾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 今日佢同我講話佢想去德國exchange,我一聽到嗰陣時有其實我非常之贊同佢去,首先佢自己有學德文,咁學德文梗係係德國學最好啦,而且德國d人民歷史嗰啲又咁正,梗係想佢見識下㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但而家一諗到德國有咁多isis又有咁多癡線難民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢去咗我一定日日擔驚受怕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但係我同時又唔想佢損失左呢個咁好嘅機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nSorry for off topic<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申:小弟係英國如果女朋友去咗德國好容易可以見到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢個亦都係其中一個想佢去嘅原因<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77d831d485d25cb29aa64a8e63c9c9f25a54a086","tid":210182,"uid":14090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T21:19:18.000Z","msg":"睇你咩城市 hamburg hanover Bremen 英文麻麻地 但berlin英文ok"},{"pid":"ae0e2e90223b80841f5bf738cb7885f519161195","tid":210182,"uid":14090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T21:20:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想知去嗰邊exchange如果德文最起碼去到咩程度先夠洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> uni上堂通常係英文定德文教書<br />\n同埋有冇話去邊個城市exchange會比較多野玩同小岐視<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係外國exchange比人歧視多數都係同人夾唔到 好睇自己 咩都接受下 人地r你去飲酒就飲下囉<br />\n<br />\n好少話一見你亞洲人就歧視 英國就另計"},{"pid":"ffb2bf1062672c571765bc6921abffe710be4db0","tid":210182,"uid":23445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T21:32:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我女人都係想去德國exchange,佢好鍾意好鍾意學新language <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n德國腸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1024b9b57ba38dcce395fd91380f2f1110407578","tid":210182,"uid":53880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T21:36:37.000Z","msg":"如果係大學offer比你既exchange基本都以英文為主先<br />\n除非你特登去果個國家上Language course<br />\n之前去左德國一轉 大城市既英文水平都幾好 <br />\n但小鎮如果長住可能真係要學熟幾句德文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27fef9266e1e38490378e0955a6839a524668c90","tid":210182,"uid":4596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T21:40:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我女人都係想去德國exchange,佢好鍾意好鍾意學新language <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n德國腸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔會啦佢都唔鍾意鬼仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 信得過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adbf6ef23042322c3aa0852392b83178ab611db3","tid":210182,"uid":10620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T06:25:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇你咩城市 hamburg hanover Bremen 英文麻麻地 但berlin英文ok</blockquote><br />\n自己德文又半桶水咁 可能真係簡Berlin<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89fdeaaf497f957e243633f774fda3a8d427bd10","tid":210182,"uid":10620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T06:28:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果係大學offer比你既exchange基本都以英文為主先<br />\n除非你特登去果個國家上Language course<br />\n之前去左德國一轉 大城市既英文水平都幾好 <br />\n但小鎮如果長住可能真係要學熟幾句德文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇啦都唔諗住去長住啦 自己maj緊德文 諗緊如果唔去德國exchange翻次就同人講自己識講fluent德文好似冇咩說服力咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d14776040ff4f590b6a31d472abf69ce652749fc","tid":210182,"uid":2659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T17:15:07.000Z","msg":"咁快有exchange去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/